 subscription_name |   status    
-------------------+-------------
 test_subscription | replicating
(1 row)

-- Clear the excluded schema list.
SELECT spock.sub_alter_options('test_subscription',
    '{"skip_schema": []}');
 sub_alter_options 
-------------------
 t
(1 row)

